      "raw_text": "1t is stated that at recent meet\ning of the newly organized Central\nLabor union, a representative of\nthe local socialist party addressed\nthe members asking them to join in\ncalling a mass meeting to protest\nagainst the treatment of the officers\nof the Western Federation of Min\ners. The labor union laid the re-\nquest on the table and refused to\nmix in the fight."
